reviewText: I have received the above order. They both play great on my DVD. My player is capable of playing PAL. These are two wonderful love stories. I think your mind must be free of sexual stereotypes to enjoy them. The key to these films is love!!
Most amazing stories! I love them!
These movies don't play at all. The message on my DVD player is "can not read disk". I've tried my blu-ray player as well as the Xbox game system. Extremely disappointed. Waste of money.
